Project description

unicodedata2

unicodedata backport/updates.

The versions of this package match Unicode versions, so unicodedata2==13.0.0 is data from Unicode 13.0.0.

Pre-compiled wheel packages are available on PyPI and can be installed via pip.

Testing

We run the tests using tox. This can be installed as usual with pip install tox.

Without any options, tox will run the tests against all of the library'starget Python versions. Any missing versions will be skipped.

To run tests against a specific python version you can use the -e option followed bya tox environment name. E.g. -e py38 will run tests against Python 3.8.For more info, check tox's documentation.

7.0.0-2

  • Compiles under Python 2.6 (and older 2.7). Patch by John Vandenberg. Fixes #2

7.0.0
